query:
SELECT cc.componentName, cc.nominalThickness, cc.actualThickness, cc.minimumThickness, cc.remainingLife
FROM componentCalculations cc
JOIN professionalReports pr ON cc.reportId = pr.id
JOIN inspections i ON pr.inspectionId = i.id
WHERE i.vesselTagNumber = '54-11-067';
